OL,3,CInheritance tax on farms can be
OL,4,C'positive,' says farmer
OL,6,FWatch ITV News' Richard Lawrence talk
OL,7,Fto Holly Purdey
OL,9,FA farmer from Somerset has called on
OL,10,Fothers to have faith in government
OL,11,Fplans to increase inheritance tax on
OL,12,Ffarms.
OL,14,FChancellor Rachel Reeves announced
OL,15,Fplans to impose a 20% inheritance tax
OL,16,Frate on farms worth more than #1
OL,17,Fmillion - prompting thousands of
OL,18,Ffarmers to march in Westminster to
OL,19,Fprotest the government's decision.
