OL,3,CInheritance tax on farms can be
OL,4,C'positive,' says farmer
OL,6,FBut Somerset based Holly Purdey
OL,7,Fbelieves the changes could be positive
OL,8,F"if managed correctly" and could lead
OL,9,Fto a decrease in the price and farms
OL,10,Fand more opportunities for new
OL,11,Fentrants to buy land.
OL,13,FHolly - who along with her husband is
OL,14,Fthe tenant of a farm near Minehead
OL,15,Fwhere they look after sheep, goats,
OL,16,Fchicken and cattle - said the changes
OL,17,Fcould enable people like her to pass
OL,18,Fsmall farms onto their children.
