OL,3,CInheritance tax on farms can be
OL,4,C'positive,' says farmer
OL,6,FShe told ITV West Country: "I think
OL,7,Fthere is a possibility that something
OL,8,Fpositive could come out of it, if it
OL,9,Fwas managed correctly.
OL,11,F"It's really important the interests
OL,12,Fof family farms are protected
OL,13,Falongside the opportunity for new
OL,14,Fentrants if the price was dropped."
OL,16,FHolly, who herself was brought up on a
OL,17,Ffarm, claims family farms are far from
OL,18,Fendangered, with "noise coming from
OL,19,Fsocial media" causing worry in farming
OL,20,Ffamilies.
