OL,3,CInheritance tax on farms can be
OL,4,C'positive,' says farmer
OL,6,F"We have a mental health crisis in
OL,7,Ffarming and it is really important
OL,8,Fthat people take time to look into
OL,9,Fthis themselves, seek advice from the
OL,10,Fcorrect people and then we can make
OL,11,Fmore forward decisions going on from
OL,12,Fthat."
OL,14,FChancellor Rachel Reeves and the
OL,15,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed have
OL,16,Fboth defended changes in inheritance
OL,17,Ftax.
