OL,3,CInheritance tax on farms can be
OL,4,C'positive,' says farmer
OL,6,FIn a joint statement they said:
OL,7,F"Farmers are the backbone of Britain,
OL,8,Fand we recognise the strength of
OL,9,Ffeeling expressed by farming and rural
OL,10,Fcommunities in recent weeks.
OL,12,F"It's why we are investing #5 billion
OL,13,Finto farming over the next two years `
OL,14,Fthe largest amount ever directed
OL,15,Ftowards sustainable food production,
OL,16,Frural economic growth and nature's
OL,17,Frecovery in our country's history."
