OL,3,CInheritance tax on farms can be
OL,4,C'positive,' says farmer
OL,6,FThe Government has said that changes
OL,7,Fensure "wealthier estates and the most
OL,8,Fvaluable farms pay their fair share to
OL,9,Finvest in our schools and health
OL,10,Fservices that farmers and families in
OL,11,Frural communities rely on."
OL,13,FHowever, farmers across the West
OL,14,FCountry have criticised the proposed
OL,15,Ftax, some fearing that large family
OL,16,Ffarms in the region will close as a
OL,17,Fresult and that farmers will have to
OL,18,Fsell off parts of their land to pay
OL,19,Fthe bills.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
